CatDescriptText: Related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "D.I.'s 'Atlantic City, USA' Thrills Patrons at Press Club Summer Revue"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gay DeHall wearing dress with double buttoned skirt, belt, and wide v-shaped lapel bodice, standing in home of Gloria Golden Grate in preparation for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A" revue held in the Press Club of the Hotel Sherwyn, another version
